            "id": "05.01.04.05",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "Costs will go up because you have duplicate environments",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "a463ae17-7d0f-4f80-b373-67aa28415f24",
            "id": "05.01.05.01",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "Leverage Azure Site Recovery for cross-region DR.",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "00c8e23b-3bcf-457e-9ff6-779ab3b4b9b2",
            "id": "05.01.05.02",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": "https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/virtual-machines/availability#azure-site-recovery"
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "Hot/Hot Design - where two active instances of the application are running and have redundant infrastructure. Both can service clients, and requests can be load-balanced between them.",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "f7f194cc-33a1-4917-ae9a-18a0d33c90ec",
            "id": "05.01.05.03",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "This is Front Door / Load Balanced / Always On approach",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "8fc8d0b2-c32a-4154-8b28-0c37e36d619d",
            "id": "05.01.05.03.01",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "Hot/Cool Design - where there is an active and passive instance of the application in two regions. One handles all client requests, but in a resiliency event, the second can be scaled out and has current data.",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "09f94c35-b4c7-4f73-9c60-0cfe8a1f56e5",
            "id": "05.01.05.04",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "Front Door / Load Balanced / Active-Passive",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "1a72b7c1-5523-4f59-84cb-e446f8658d6e",
            "id": "05.01.05.04.01",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "Hot/Cold Design - where there is a single instance in the primary region, and replicated instances of VMs in a secondary region. Failover can occur by turning these replicated instances into active.",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "9b2357a9-6ad4-47cf-935f-c0c0abf00754",
            "id": "05.01.05.05",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "This is the Azure Site Recovery approach",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "f58aa9a7-603b-4e8f-a9e1-6df7478af646",
            "id": "05.01.05.05.01",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "Fast Deploy Design - where you use IaC to rapidly deploy into another region that already has your data.",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "0fb7dd6e-75d7-4d90-a95d-c14c6a0f7b10",
            "id": "05.01.05.06",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Multi-Region Resiliency",
            "subcategory": "Multi Region Mindset",
            "text": "Requires the data solution to already have replicated data - such as Azure SQL backups or geo-availability, or an existing Always On Availability Group.",
            "waf": "Reliability",
            "guid": "49d086d9-98ac-4bf4-b045-13c0a8e52c86",
            "id": "05.01.05.06.01",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
