            "guid": "d6f88433-7ff0-48d0-9a3c-0c6157a50b95",
            "id": "05.01.06.01.05",
            "cost": 1,
            "severity": "Medium",
            "link": ""
        },
        {
            "category": "Backup and Recovery",
            "subcategory": "Back up Vs. DR - Related scenarios, but not the same",
            "text": "High Recovery Time because the data often has to be restored, sorted through, and then reattached.",
